<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>A4 Paper Size with Shade - Centered Content</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 0;
        }

        html,
        body {
            width: 210mm;
            height: 297mm;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .content {
            width: 80%;
            height: 80%;
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="w-full h-full px-10 py-4">
        <div class="w-full p-16 flex justify-center flex-col gap-5">
            <div class="text-[3rem] text-left font-[800] text-[#4036F4] py-5">
                House of Web3
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">First of itâ€™s kind;</p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">
                    Confluence between Artificial & Human intelligence to deliver best
                    ROI on influencer campaigns.
                </p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem]">
                    Tired of the spammy, spray-and-pray approach to influencer
                    marketing? So are we.
                </p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">
                    With our proprietary algorithms, we can identify and activate just
                    the right influencers for your project, whether you need pre-launch
                    hype-builders or post-launch credibility boosters.
                </p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">
                    We go beyond solo influencer sponsorships to orchestrate integrated
                    campaigns with coordinated engagement across influencer networks,
                    communities, and platforms.
                </p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] font-[600] pt-4 italic">
                    House of Web3 specializes in influencer marketing campaign execution
                    and strategy, focusing on long-term brand authority and precisely
                    targeted campaigns.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-[3rem] text-left font-[800] text-[#4036F4] py-5">
                Overview
            </div>

            <div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">
                    During our meeting, you mentioned your main objective is to create a
                    successful campaign that will consider your corporate identity and
                    find an influencer to promote your project.
                </p>

                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-4">
                    House of Web3 is a part of the world's most impactful influencer
                    network and our marketing experts have a wide range of skills that
                    will help you advertise your brand in the best way.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-[1.5rem] font-[700] text-gray-700 pt-5">
                Pain Points:
            </div>

            <ol class="list-disc">
                <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-1">
                    <span class="font-[700]">Hype vs. Impact:</span> Tired of empty hype
                    campaigns that fizzle out? We create sustainable brand authority
                    with long-term impact.
                </li>

                <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-1">
                    <span class="font-[700]">Targeting Nightmare:</span> Tired of empty hype
                    campaigns that fizzle out? We create sustainable brand authority
                    with long-term impact.
                </li>

                <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-1">
                    <span class="font-[700]">Engagement Woes:</span> Posts that scream
                    "sponsored"? We craft organic-looking content that sparks authentic
                    conversations and drives viral action.
                </li>

                <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-1">
                    <span class="font-[700]">ROI Blues:</span> Unsure of your campaign's
                    return? We deliver measurable results that translate directly to
                    your bottom line.
                </li>
            </ol>

            <div class="pt-20">
                <p class="pt-3 text-black text-[1.5rem] font-[500] italic">
                    In the next few chapters, we will explain further the details of our
                    plan and how to address the above mentioned Pain Points.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="pt-10">
                <p class="pt-3 text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem]">
                    In the next few chapters, we will explain further the details of our
                    plan and how to address the above mentioned Pain Points.
                </p>

                <ol class="list-disc">
                    <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-2">
                        <span class="font-[700]">Hero Influencers:</span> These highly
                        respected influencers are known for their unparalleled credibility
                        and authentic engagement. While they may collaborate less
                        frequently and the engagement may not be the best amongst all
                        influencers, their involvement lends credibility to any campaign.
                    </li>

                    <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-2">
                        <span class="font-[700]">Hype Influencers:</span>
                        With a knack for frequent collaborations and a mixed base of
                        credibility, hype influencers are masters at driving engagement.
                        Their strategic use of boosted engagement amplifies campaign
                        visibility and reach. At the same time, their turnaround time is
                        lesser hence giving a launchpad for projects to launch quickly.
                    </li>

                    <li class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem] pt-2">
                        <span class="font-[700]">RTM Influencers:</span>
                        The hallmark of RTM influencers is their ability to rapidly scale
                        campaigns through frequent collaborations. By leveraging automated
                        engagement techniques using bots, they can quickly propel content
                        to the top of algorithms. The algo doesn't differentiate between
                        bots & humans when it comes to engagement. What it does rather is
                        increase visibility across feeds of users interested in similar
                        topic.
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div
                class="text-[1.5rem] text-center font-[800] text-gray-700 py-16 italic">
                By strategically aligning all 3, we help create a story telling angle
                and drive narratives by effectively harnesses the power of algorithms
                that favour high-engagement content. The result is dramatically
                enhanced visibility, reach, and impact for your campaigns which means
                better ROI.
            </div>

            <div class="text-[3rem] text-center font-[800] text-[#4036F4] py-5">
                Project Investment
            </div>

            <div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem]">
                    Your investment includes everything we spoke about in our meeting and
                    the previous chapters of this proposal. It covers the full influencer
                    marketing package, including the standard rate for influencer posting.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="text-gray-700 text-[1.5rem]">
                    The cost may increase depending on your influencer preferences.
                </p>
            </div>

            <% if (showInfluencersList) { %>
            <div class="py-16">
                <div class="w-full h-fit border-[0.5px] border-gray-500 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="w-full h-fit bg-[#4036F4] rounded-t-xl">
                        <div class="pt-20 px-10 pb-10 flex w-full justify-between">
                            <div class="text-white text-[1rem] font-[700]">
                                Influencers List
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-white text-[1rem] flex gap-2">
                                <div>
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 font-[700]">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>

                                <div>SUBTOTAL $<%= influencersSubtotal %></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Influencer Table Change  -->
                    <div id="Div15000" class="flex flex-col justify-between w-full">
                        <!-- heading -->
                        <div class="w-full pt-10 pb-4 px-3 font-[700] flex text-gray-700">
                            <div class="w-[60%]">Description</div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">Item</div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">Price</div>
                        </div>
                        <% items.forEach(function(item) { %>
                        <div class="w-full py-6 px-3 font-[700] flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 border-t border-t-gray-600">
                            <div class="w-[60%]">
                                <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-2 font-[700] text-gray-700">
                                    <div>
                                        <a href="<%= item.product.link %>" class="underline" target="_blank"><%= item.product.name %></a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div><%= item.product.category_name %> | <%= item.product.geography %> | <%= item.product.subscribers %> Subscribers | <%= item.product.content_type %></div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">$<%= item.product.price.toFixed(2) %></div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">$<%= item.product.price.toFixed(2) %></div>
                        </div>
                        <% }) %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <% if (showPackagesList) { %>
            <div class="py-16">
                <div class="w-full h-fit border-[0.5px] border-gray-500 rounded-xl">
                    <div class="w-full h-fit bg-[#4036F4] rounded-t-xl">
                        <div class="pt-20 px-10 pb-10 flex w-full justify-between">
                            <div class="text-white text-[1rem] font-[700]">
                                PR Packages
                            </div>

                            <div class="text-white text-[1rem] flex gap-2">
                                <div>
                                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-7 h-7 font-[700]">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m19.5 8.25-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"/>
                                    </svg>
                                </div>

                                <div>SUBTOTAL $<%= packagesSubtotal %></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Packages heading -->
                    <div id="Div8000" class="flex flex-col justify-between w-full overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="w-full pt-10 pb-4 px-3 font-[700] flex text-gray-700 overflow-hidden">
                            <div class="w-[80%]">Description</div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">Price</div>
                        </div>
                        <% packages.forEach(function(pkg) { %>
                        <div class="w-full py-6 px-3 font-[700] flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-200 border-t border-t-gray-600">
                            <div class="w-[80%]">
                                <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-2 text-black font-[400]">
                                    <div class="pb-5 font-[700] text-gray-700"><%= pkg.header %></div>
                                    <% pkg.packages.forEach(function(packageItem) { %>
                                    <div>
                                        <a href="<%= packageItem.link %>" class="underline" target="_blank"><%= packageItem.media %></a> | <%= packageItem.format %> | <%= packageItem.monthlyTraffic %>
                                    </div>
                                    <% }) %>
                                    <div class="py-3 text-[1rem]">
                                        <p><%= pkg.text1 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text2 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text3 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text4 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text5 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text6 %></p>
                                        <p><%= pkg.text7 %></p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="w-[20%]">$<%= pkg.cost %></div>
                        </div>
                        <% }) %>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <% } %>

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center">
                <div class="w-[60%] h-fit bg-[#4036F4] rounded-xl flex flex-col gap-3 p-5 py-10">
                    <div class="text-white border-b-[0.4px] border-b-white py-3 flex justify-between">
                        <div>Total Excluding Tax</div>
                        <div>$<%= totalExcludingTax %></div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="text-white border-b-[0.4px] border-b-white flex py-3 justify-between">
                        <div>Management Fee: 25%</div>
                        <div>$<%= managementFee %></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-white border-b-[0.4px] text-[1.5rem] font-[700] border-b-white py-3 flex justify-between">
                        <div>Total</div>
                        <div>$<%= total %></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full flex justify-center py-5">
                <div class="text-[4rem] font-[800] text-[#4036F4]">
                    Results that matter!
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
